'''[[喬治亞|喬治亞]]'''是一個[[議會制|議會制]]的多黨制民主國家，[[喬治亞總統|喬治亞總統]]是國家元首，[[喬治亞總理|喬治亞總理]]則是政府領導人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.parliament.ge/files/68_1944_951190_CONSTIT_27_12.06.pdf |title=Constitution of Georgia |accessdate=2015-12-12 |archive-date=2017-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110075034/http://www.parliament.ge/files/68_1944_951190_CONSTIT_27_12.06.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。立法權由政府和國會所有。喬治亞國內有[[阿佈哈茲|阿佈哈茲]]、[[阿扎爾|阿扎爾]]兩個自治共和國及[[南奧塞梯自治州|南奧塞梯自治州]]，其中阿布哈茲和[[南奧塞梯|南奧塞梯]]單方面宣布獨立，但喬治亞拒絕承認。現在喬治亞國內有實施[[君主立憲制|君主立憲制]]的討論<ref name="GeorgiaToday">Zaza Jgharkava (October 18, 2007). [http://www.georgiatoday.ge/article_details.php?id=3733  Will a Constitutional Monarchy Be Restored in Georgia?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.georgiatoday.ge/article_details.php?id=3733 |date=20150111014408 }}. Georgia Today, Issue #379.</ref><ref name="Lomsadze">Giorgi Lomsadze (December 18, 2007). [http://www.eurasianet.net/departments/insight/articles/eav101207a.shtml Time for a King for Georgia?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eurasianet.net/departments/insight/articles/eav101207a.shtml |date=20080121170547 }}. EurasiaNet Civil Society.</ref>。

